me.dpohvar.powernbt.api
Class NBTManager

java.lang.Object
  me.dpohvar.powernbt.api.NBTManager

public class NBTManager
extends Object

PowerNBT API.
This class has methods to read and write NBT tags.
NBTCompound is used to work with NBTTagCompound,
NBTList is used to work with NBTTagList,
String is used to work with NBTTagString,
all other NBT tags represents by primitive values.

Since:
0.7.1

parseMojangson

public Object parseMojangson(String value)
Parse mojangson string.
This method can return:
byte, short, int, long, float, double, byte[], String, int[],
NBTList or NBTCompound
Examples:
     manager.parseMojangson("12s\\"); // 12 short
     manager.parseMojangson("{foo:bar}"); // NBTCompound

Parameters:
value - String in Mojangson format
Returns:
Parse result
Since:
0.8.2
